<h2>08 圆形的延续</h2>
<p><strong>圆形</strong>，不用多说，我想经常看我文章伙伴应该知道，我之前有提到过圆形趋势。圆形之所以受到广泛设计师的喜爱，不亚于<strong>它本身图形亲和力很强</strong>，而且<strong>适应性很强</strong>。基本大部分设计都能用。</p>
<p>代表作品<strong>苹果发布新品运营</strong>主视觉也有运用。</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class=" aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/10/REd3i2VyPGwajK2yZSgW.jpeg" width="505" height="615" /></p>
<p><strong>北京服装学院</strong>毕业设计展的<strong>主视觉</strong>。</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class=" aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/10/vg5o69Pnj6gUzPUwEQlD.png" width="502" height="893" /></p>
<p>其他优秀案例。</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class=" aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/10/AMPUG4id0Jvz6h7BBWo0.png" width="500" height="704" /></p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class=" aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/10/bOWmxfU1oNoZrClrkAFy.png" width="704" height="504" /></p>
<p>在UI设计中也是运用广泛。</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class=" aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/10/u0aijUHA81m9i9QvhkW1.png" width="706" height="404" /></p>
